title: PMDG 777 landed in MSFS marketplace #msfs2020 #pmdg #aircraft
description:
This week, the marketplace has seen the arrival of several aircraft, including PMDG's Boeing 777. Previously available only through PMDG, it is now accessible via the marketplace, extending its availability to Xbox users. The Boeing 777 represents a significant advancement in aircraft design, offering a substantial challenge for enthusiasts. It is certainly worth considering for purchase if you're looking to elevate your flying experience.
